author: awiner
msg: Support multiple feature values per param
- Gadget Features are now a Multimap.  Feature.getParam() aids in existing get-a-single-param cases
- Templates now support multiple template libraries per gadget
- The content rewriting feature has *not* been updated to be 0.9 compliant, but that's now possible
